    },
    {
      "id": "panel1_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 35, "y": 795,
      "width": 530, "height": 460,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "text": "user_instances : Dict[str, DuckDBPyConnection]\nuser_locks     : Dict[str, asyncio.Lock]\nsession_meta   : Dict[str, SessionMetadata]\n\n• Lock lazy-initialized on first RPC call\n• One DuckDB connection per user\n  (new LoadFile replaces existing)\n• TTL eviction via background asyncio.Task\n  — evict after SESSION_TTL_MINUTES idle\n\nSessionResume order (pod restart):\n  1. Load originals from  data/\n  2. Load exports  from   derived/\n\nSessionMetadata:\n  user_id      : str\n  files        : List[FileRecord]\n  last_accessed: datetime\n  created_at   : datetime",
      "originalText": "user_instances : Dict[str, DuckDBPyConnection]\nuser_locks     : Dict[str, asyncio.Lock]\nsession_meta   : Dict[str, SessionMetadata]\n\n• Lock lazy-initialized on first RPC call\n• One DuckDB connection per user\n  (new LoadFile replaces existing)\n• TTL eviction via background asyncio.Task\n  — evict after SESSION_TTL_MINUTES idle\n\nSessionResume order (pod restart):\n  1. Load originals from  data/\n  2. Load exports  from   derived/\n\nSessionMetadata:\n  user_id      : str\n  files        : List[FileRecord]\n  last_accessed: datetime\n  created_at   : datetime",
