      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "text": "ExecuteQuery  (server-side streaming)",
      "originalText": "ExecuteQuery  (server-side streaming)",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "seed": 100041, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 100041,
      "isDeleted": false, "index": "b4",
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 0, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "panel4_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1775, "y": 795,
      "width": 610, "height": 460,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Streaming protocol (oneof):\n\n  Msg 1:  QueryHeader\n    col_names : repeated string\n    col_types : repeated string\n\n  Msg 2…N:  QueryRow\n    json : string  (batch_size = 100)\n\nFlow:\n  1. Acquire user_lock (asyncio)\n  2. SQLGuardrails.validate(sql)\n  3. conn.execute(sql)  → cursor\n  4. yield QueryHeader(cols)\n  5. loop: fetch batch → yield QueryRow\n  6. Release lock\n\nTimeout:  asyncio.wait_for(60s)\n\nError codes:\n  INVALID_ARGUMENT — SQL not allowed\n  NOT_FOUND        — no session\n  DEADLINE_EXCEEDED— 60s timeout\n  INTERNAL         — DuckDB error",
      "originalText": "Streaming protocol (oneof):\n\n  Msg 1:  QueryHeader\n    col_names : repeated string\n    col_types : repeated string\n\n  Msg 2…N:  QueryRow\n    json : string  (batch_size = 100)\n\nFlow:\n  1. Acquire user_lock (asyncio)\n  2. SQLGuardrails.validate(sql)\n  3. conn.execute(sql)  → cursor\n  4. yield QueryHeader(cols)\n  5. loop: fetch batch → yield QueryRow\n  6. Release lock\n\nTimeout:  asyncio.wait_for(60s)\n\nError codes:\n  INVALID_ARGUMENT — SQL not allowed\n  NOT_FOUND        — no session\n  DEADLINE_EXCEEDED— 60s timeout\n  INTERNAL         — DuckDB error",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "seed": 100042, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 100042,
      "isDeleted": false, "index": "b5",
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 0, "link": null, "locked": false
