    {
      "id": "envvars_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1555, "y": 1350,
      "width": 830, "height": 395,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Variable               Default    Description\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────\nGRPC_PORT              50051      Port for gRPC server\nSTORAGE_ROOT           /data      Persistent volume mount\nMAX_FILE_MB            100        Max upload size (MB)\nMAX_SESSIONS           1000       Max concurrent users\nSESSION_TTL_MINUTES    60         Idle eviction threshold\nGRPC_MAX_WORKERS       10         asyncio thread pool\nBATCH_SIZE             100        Rows per QueryRow msg\nHEALTH_PORT            8080       HTTP health endpoint\n\nStack:\n  Python 3.11\n  grpcio + grpcio-tools\n  grpcio-health-checking\n  duckdb\n  aiofiles\n  openpyxl  (XLSX support)\n\nDeploy: Railway  (persistent volume → STORAGE_ROOT)\nHealth: grpc.health.v1.Health  (standard protocol)",
      "originalText": "Variable               Default    Description\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────\nGRPC_PORT              50051      Port for gRPC server\nSTORAGE_ROOT           /data      Persistent volume mount\nMAX_FILE_MB            100        Max upload size (MB)\nMAX_SESSIONS           1000       Max concurrent users\nSESSION_TTL_MINUTES    60         Idle eviction threshold\nGRPC_MAX_WORKERS       10         asyncio thread pool\nBATCH_SIZE             100        Rows per QueryRow msg\nHEALTH_PORT            8080       HTTP health endpoint\n\nStack:\n  Python 3.11\n  grpcio + grpcio-tools\n  grpcio-health-checking\n  duckdb\n  aiofiles\n  openpyxl  (XLSX support)\n\nDeploy: Railway  (persistent volume → STORAGE_ROOT)\nHealth: grpc.health.v1.Health  (standard protocol)",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.4,
